query:
UPDATE tee_proof_generation_details
            SET
                status = $1,
                updated_at = NOW(),
                prover_taken_at = NOW()
            WHERE
                tee_type = $2
                AND l1_batch_number = (
                    SELECT
                        proofs.l1_batch_number
                    FROM
                        tee_proof_generation_details AS proofs
                    WHERE
                        (
                            proofs.status = $3
                            OR (
                                proofs.status = $1
                                AND proofs.prover_taken_at < NOW() - $4::INTERVAL
                            )
                        )
                        AND proofs.l1_batch_number >= $5
                    ORDER BY
                        l1_batch_number ASC
                    LIMIT
                        1
                    FOR UPDATE
                        SKIP LOCKED
                )
            RETURNING
                tee_proof_generation_details.l1_batch_number
